=====
sms16
=====

The library implements sending SMS messages via `sms16.ru <https://new.sms16.ru>`_ service.

Installation
------------

:code:`$ pip install sms16`

Settings
--------

Add the following environment variables:

SMS16_API_KEY - Your `API key <https://new.sms16.ru/api/>`_

SMS16_LOGIN - `Your Login <https://new.sms16.ru/register/>`_

SMS16_SENDER_NAME - Approved `sender name <https://new.sms16.ru/senders/>`_

Using
-----

:code:`from sms16.sms import Sms`

:code:`sms = Sms()`

:code:`print(sms.balance())`

:code:`print(sms.send(phone="PHONE NUMBER", text="MESSAGE TEXT"))`

:code:`print(sms.status(ids=["5650905190972394390001", "5650905190972394390002"]))`


